<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV35">
<l>ampulāvu mīṉumāki yāmaiyāki yāḻiyār</l>
<l>tampirāṉu mākimikka taṉpumikka taṉṟiyuṅ</l>
<l>komparāvu nuṇmaruṅku lāyarmātar piḷḷaiyāy</l>
<l>empirāṉu māyavaṇṇa meṉkolōvem mīcaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[You] were excellent becoming a fish that roams in water [and] a tortoise</l>
<l>[despite] being the Master with the discus; You excelled in affection.</l>
<l>Besides, how is it [You] are our Lord, [despite] being the child of a cowherdess</l>
<l>with a fine waist that challenges a [young] twig?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
